flowchart LR
    subgraph Onboarding
        A[Customer Portal] -->|POST /v1/customers| B[onboarding-service]
        B -->|Couchbase Upsert| C[(Couchbase: customers)]
        B -->|Produce CustomerOnboarded| D[(Kafka: customer_events)]
        D -->|Consumed by| E[billing-service]
    end
    E -->|Initialize billing account| F[(MySQL: invoices)]
